 "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAA AWLIYYAA-ILLAAHE WA ASFE-YAAA-E-HE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA OMANAAA-ILLAAHE WA A-JIBBAA-E-HE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA ANSAARIL-LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MA-HAALLE MA’RE-FATIL LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MASAA-KENE ZIKRIL-LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAA MUZHE-REE AMRIL-LAAHE WA NAHYE-HI. AS-SALAAMO A’LAD DO-AA’TE ILAL-LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAL MUSTAQIR-REENA FEE MARZAATIL-LAAHE.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَوْلِیَآئِ اللهِ وَاَصْفِیَآئِهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اُمَنَآئِ اللهِ وَاَحِبَّائِهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَنْصَارِ اللهِ وَخُلَفَآئِهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَحَآلِّ مَعْرِفَۃِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَسَاكِنِ ذِكْرِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُظْهِرِیْ اَمْرِ اللهِ وَ نَهْیِهٖ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الدُّعَاۃِ اِلَی اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْمُسْتَقِرِّیْنَ فِیْ مَرْضَاتِ اللهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign